Seq2.CallerContent: Yes, sir. Can I give him a minute? Yeah, of course. You can speak to her. She's available. Let me transfer the call and you have a great day. Yeah. Yeah.

Seq3.ReceiverContent: Hello. You have reached the nurse line. If this is an emergency, please hang up and dial 9-1-1.

Seq4.ReceiverContent: If you're calling for a prescription refill, please leave a detailed message with the drug name, the milligrams, and your pharmacy information.

Seq5.ReceiverContent: Please allow 72 hours for your refills to be processed. Leave us a message and we'll get back to you as soon as we can. Thank you and have a good day.
